<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Rust2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Rust,</orth> vb. 1) intr. to gather rust: <bibl n="shak. lll 1.2.187" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 2, 187</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. aww 4.3.373" default="NO" valid="yes">All's IV, 3, 373</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h5 5.2.46" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 2, 46</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 2h6 3.2.198" default="NO" valid="yes">H6B III, 2, 198</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 1.3.51" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C I, 3, 51</bibl> <cit><quote>(this thy son's blood shall r. upon my weapon).</quote> <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.170" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 3, 170</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. per 2.2.54" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. II, 2, 54</bibl>.<lb />2) tr. to make rusty: <cit><quote>this peace is nothing, but to r. iron,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 4.5.234" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. IV, 5, 234</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>the dew will r. them,</quote> <bibl n="shak. oth 1.2.59" default="NO" valid="yes">Oth. I, 2, 59</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>